Param sharding         P() (replicated)        Each GPU holds full copy
Gradient sync          Hierarchical AllReduce  pmean(gpus) -> pmean(nodes)
Level 1 (NVLink)       jax.lax.pmean           Intra-node (4 GPUs), ~478 GB/s
